             </font> 
            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">Each day for the next few days, several servers will be coming down for scheduled maintenance. From EQ Live's Scheduled Downtime Page here are the specifics: <br />
On Wednesday, October 2nd, at 3AM PDT, (10AM GMT), the Rodcet Nife, Prexus, and Quellious Servers will be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 9 hours. <br />
<br />
On Thursday, October 3rd, at 3AM PDT, (10AM GMT), the Tunare, Brell Serilis, and Veeshan Servers will be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 9 hours. <br />
<br />
<b>On Friday, October 4th, at 3AM PDT, (10AM GMT), the Xegony, Rathe, and Bertoxxulous Servers will be brought down for scheduled maintenance. The estimated downtime is 9 hours.</b><br />
<br />
-The EverQuest Operations Team</font></p>
             
